These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, chef
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, skateboard
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the coach is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | collecting       | hiking |
| Job         | chef | coach  |
| Sport       | rugby    | handball    |
| Transport   | skateboard       | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, project-manager
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, family
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the librarian is on the far left##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | fanta |
| Job           | librarian | project-manager      |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | musical      |
| Sport         | golf | basketball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, plum
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, punk
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bus
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up  |
| Food          | artichoke    | plum   |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | metal   |
| Transport     | bus     | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: avocado, banana
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, d&b
1. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | sprite       | mirinda |
| Food          | banana         | avocado    |
| Job           | fisherman | project-manager    |
| Music-Genre   | funk           | d&b   |

