.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, broccoli
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, electronic
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, american
2 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla
1. the american is the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the american is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | papaya | broccoli |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | electronic      |
| Nationality   | japanese | american    |
| Pet           | mouse    | chinchilla    |

