.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, librarian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, family
2 different pets are kept: fish, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the architect is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the architect is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the owner of the fish is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | librarian | architect     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller          | family |
| Pet           | fish          | hamster    |
| Transport     | taxi            | quad-bike       |

 